result.name: Lung Hin Restaurant

reviews.text: Very nice chicken & lamb hot pot

A local-local restaurant that served nice Hongkie food; their breakfast, fish fillet was wonderful. The place might look mundane or somewhat untidy, but I would not worry too much about the outlook of a restaurant, as long as the price was reasonable and the food was tasty and safe.

Recently Ling Hin was registered to Eatigo and so before visiting, you might want to check if they offered any discount.
食物ok ！平靚正😋 可惜地方污糟,只係感覺到去咗大排檔咁啦!😂最好都係外賣送到！💪
不計地方环境，其它食物及招待都可以接受。👍👍👍
